div.span12
  div.hero-unit(style='padding:15px')
    h2 Asterank is an economic and scientific catalog of over 500,000 asteroids in our solar system.

  div.welcome-blurb.alert.alert-info
    <a class="close" data-dismiss="alert" href="#">×</a>
    p With all the recent hype around asteroid mining, I wanted real numbers.  How realistic are the trillion dollar estimates?  What about the costs and overhead?

    p I've attempted to calculate or infer things like asteroid mass and composition.  I’ve collected data on their orbits from sources including NASA and JPL.  Using this information, I estimate the costs and rewards of commercially exploiting rocks in space.

    p Take a look at the results:
      ul
        li Best overall (most cost-effective)
        li Most accessible
        li Most profitable

    p There is $$ worth of rock out there.

  div.row
    div.span12.well
      form.form-inline(style='margin:0')
        div
          span Search top
          select#top_num(style='margin:0 5px 0').input-small
            option 100
            option 1,000
            option 10,000
            option 100,000
            option 1,000,000
          span  asteroids sorted by
          select#top_sort(style='margin:0 5px 0').input-medium
            option most cost effective
            option most valuable
            option closest
          input#submit.btn.btn-primary(type='submit')

        //
          div(style='margin: 5px 0 0')
            p or
          div(style='margin: 5px 0 0')
            span Search for an object:
            input#search(type='text', style='margin: 0 5px 0')

          div(style='margin: 5px 0 0')
            input#submit.btn.btn-primary(type='submit')

